<bibRefCitation pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bechyné">Bechyne</normalizedToken>
(1957
</bibRefCitation>
: 181). This species was transferred to 
<taxonomicName authority="Bechyne, 1959" authorityName="Bechyne" authorityYear="1959" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Afrorestia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afrorestia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Afrorestia</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Bechyné">Bechyne</normalizedToken>
by 
<bibRefCitation pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
Biondi and 
<normalizedToken originalValue="D’Alessandro">D'Alessandro</normalizedToken>
(2010a
</bibRefCitation>
: 403).
</paragraph>
